  dialogue:
  - I can't be going out there anymore. There's something prowling the waters.
  - It attacked the boat!
  - Tellin' fibs now, lad?
  - I know what I saw. You can check the boat for damage.
  - We should just head to the mainland to get our food.
  - Ye won't be gettin' yer money if ye leave.
  - It's just a quick stop.
  - It's yer choice, lad.
  - Just know what ye would lose.
